#: ../../c-api/set.rst:122
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Return the length of a :class:`set` or :class:`frozenset` object. Equivalent"
" to ``len(anyset)``.  Raises a :exc:`SystemError` if *anyset* is not a "
":class:`set`, :class:`frozenset`, or an instance of a subtype."
